<item>
            <title>[LU-10031] Interop: sanity-hsm test_26a: request on 0x2000088d5:0x2a:0x0 is not SUCCEED on mds1</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10031</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah_lw &amp;lt;wei3.liu@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/43ddb5d8-9c2a-11e7-b778-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/43ddb5d8-9c2a-11e7-b778-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_26a failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;request on 0x2000088d5:0x2a:0x0 is not SUCCEED on mds1
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;server: 2.9.0 RHEL7.3&lt;br/&gt;
client: 2.10.1 RHEL7.4&lt;br/&gt;
test log&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== sanity-hsm test 26a: Remove Archive On Last Unlink (RAoLU) policy ================================= 07:26:55 (1505633215)
CMD: trevis-52vm7 /usr/sbin/lctl get_param -n mdt.lustre-MDT0000.hsm.remove_archive_on_last_unlink
trevis-52vm7: error: get_param: param_path &apos;mdt/lustre-MDT0000/hsm/remove_archive_on_last_unlink&apos;: No such file or directory
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity-hsm 26a&lt;/p&gt;</description>
